Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:05.68,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導かれ出逢い 交差するSaison
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.60,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背中合わせの光と影のように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:17.29,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強く引かれる　Mystification
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:23.04,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳元で囁き呼ぶ声に振り向けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:28.89,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かぬうち開かれていたトビラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:34.65,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少しの偶然と必然をつなぐように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:40.06,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動き始めた二つのHistoire
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:52.57,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと果てなく続いて行く

Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:48.39,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很久以前就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:53.96,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很久之前就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.46,0:00:59.90,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛行走在看不见的线上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.07,0:01:05.68,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被牵引的邂逅 交错的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:11.60,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一纸相隔的光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:17.29,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被强烈吸引的Mystification
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.52,0:01:23.04,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在耳边轻轻细语 转头一看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:28.89,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经意间已经打开的门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:34.65,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小小的偶然与必然有着不可分割的联系一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:40.06,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与开始变化的两段历史一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:52.57,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远 无尽地持续下去

Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:40.33,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:49.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新たな旅立ち 迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:59.71,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失いかけていた　Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:04.69,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼び覚ましたconfined　in you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:14.38,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共にした日々を強く握り緊め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.74,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互いに寄り添い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:28.65,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れる事などない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:34.07,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇が二人分かつとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:39.35,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確かな鼓動が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.40,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう告げているから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:48.18,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再び出会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:24:00.55,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想いよ　どうか君と共に

Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:40.33,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.48,0:22:49.67,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎接新的启程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:59.71,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐着失落之物　Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:04.69,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒被囚禁中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:14.38,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力握紧朝夕共处的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.88,0:23:19.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Wherever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.74,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要互相靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:28.65,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就无害怕之事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:34.07,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使黑暗终将分开你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:39.35,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明确的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:43.40,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣告了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:48.18,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到与你再次相遇那天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.68,0:24:00.55,op_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望这份思念能伴你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:12.55,op_chi,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我來到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…Phantom嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲小姐 已經在裡面了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.30,0:02:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個箱子突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽西爾老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這是怎麼了 為什麼會在箱子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為一名教師不能對學生的危機置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我拼上性命進行的潛入調查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請冷靜一下 妳說的學生是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說 維多利加同學有麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加同學又被父親傳喚去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳就待在這 賽西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再繼續涉入了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺似乎和往常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為是在箱子裡 所以不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城君？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:47.68,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(658,546)}受Phantom的幽靈指引
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管妳身在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管將要到來的暴風雨有多麼猛烈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你為什麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…你真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會找到妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…維多利加 慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去父親 亞伯特·德·布洛瓦侯爵那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得好 我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.03,0:06:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是讓妳的力量為我等所用之時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我思考過了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼靈異部會在那麼多年後還想揭發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可·蘿絲事件的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你們已經有所頭緒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有確定性的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想找到證據 並以此抓住犯人的把柄對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後 得到更高的地位以及權力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個國家擁有此等影響力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正是這起事件的真正犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才不愧是我親愛的灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可·蘿絲事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前一次大戰之前不久 1914春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從法國來了一名使者想面見可可王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王陛下將身在鄉間別墅的王妃接進了王宮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在房間被人發現時 王妃已經是一具無頭屍體了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.36,0:07:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人在之前進過王妃的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是當然 他沒有持有任何可疑的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在幾乎同一時刻 在王妃的鄉間別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在目擊者中也有科學院的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後事件就陷入了僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要維多利加來解決這個事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不解決這件事的話 她就無法回學園去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是父親大人的決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得她會有無法解決的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用如此擔心啊 小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片…混沌的碎片聚齊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報紙上的報導 當時的調查報告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料都應該收集齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這種程度的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加早就已經知道真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去收集起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的話就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不將碎片帶來 維多利加就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要和維多利加一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著我 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道柯蒂麗亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂麗亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 柯蒂麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這個人果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加的…母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是16年前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不錯的舞女啊 突然就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…她母親待過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這地方 維多利加她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 剛剛有個女孩子也看著這張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長的非常像 一瞬間還以為是本人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王妃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼王妃的照片會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩是尼可蕾·露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和可可王妃長的很像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人叫做「平民區的藍薔薇」 是個非常有人氣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民區的…藍薔薇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很開朗的好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子也無緣無故不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在這行裡也是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.36,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快將謎解開吧 灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的 混沌的碎片還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料已經全部集齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上根本沒有灰色之狼不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也要集齊了碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這些的話就算想再構成也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招秘書？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 1900年的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多24年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個嗎 我記得很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像條件是金髪藍瞳的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連腳的尺寸也指定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面試結束後 房間就處理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群奇怪的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫尼可蕾·露露的女演員…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去應徵了剛剛那個秘書的募集後 就這樣失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 果然很可疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微調查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 這也是為了維多利加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…「平民區的藍薔薇」?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的和事件有關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一種有關係的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什麼時候 我看見她坐上了一輛豪華的馬車哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可蕾不再上臺表演 也已經有10年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是成了不知道是什麼地方的貴族還是有錢人的情婦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.92,0:13:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我也聽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來尼可蕾不見 也已經有10年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去應徵秘書 貴族的情婦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.45,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同學 讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很難得啊 也要買點特產回去給蘇菲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給蘇菲小姐的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們經常一起來購物 要是知道我一個人來了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會生氣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲小姐的話 現在就在蘇瓦倫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 她來看可可·蘿絲的那個戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是坐她的摩托車來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不約我一起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將相處10年的老友扔在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼和久城同學一起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相處10年的老友？妳們是在哪裡認識的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭久城同學 所以不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.93,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那個…老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲就更討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是得感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 什麼時候會出場呢 可可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可蕾·露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說您是她的超級fan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.48,0:15:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以真是個大打擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說她死了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼你們不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼可蕾她已經死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 上面寫著 1900年亡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…尼克蕾小姐失蹤那年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是秘書募集那年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在那10年後被人目擊到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請現在馬上住手 就算做這種事也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也好好看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女兒 你的妹妹身上所寄宿的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用藥草使感覺變得敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而單調的回音和蠟燭的搖晃不過是為了增強效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼靈異啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不完全是科學嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們既沒票 劇場旁邊還有守衛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊 久城君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官應該會來才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.58,0:16:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開謎團吧 灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.72,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在儀式結束前 不許離開這房間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師妳就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了 久城君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰色之狼 解開謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答 犯人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人手法呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對抗我時的那份氣勢去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:17:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布萊恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了 住…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開燈 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狼在裡面這扇門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了 太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這個事件…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不牽連我 妳…妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不也挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.35,0:20:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個漸漸捲入妳所有一切的 麻煩的…朋友存在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖的儀式被玷污了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個人趕出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 就算現在於此掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法從父親的束縛中掙脫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而展現力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會解開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來解開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會解開可可·蘿絲事件的謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給美麗的狼之母 送上祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會想要調查尼可蕾·露露？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我覺得這事應該能讓妳開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為無聊秀才的你來說算是做得不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表揚你一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人的許可下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.14,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 妳想去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去墓地 挖出尼可蕾·露露的棺材
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可·蘿絲的舞臺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的帷幕終於要拉開了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可 就讓我在妳的人生裡裝飾上花朵吧
